OL,3,CUK net migration hits lowest level
OL,4,Csince 2012, excluding pandemic
OL,6,FNet migration to the UK has dropped to
OL,7,F171,000 in the year to December 2025,
OL,8,Fthe lowest since 2012 excluding the
OL,9,Fpandemic.
OL,11,FIt is the first time the estimate `
OL,12,Fwhich is the difference between the
OL,13,Fnumber of people moving to the UK and
OL,14,Fthe number of people leaving the
OL,15,Fcountry ` has fallen below 200,000
OL,16,Fsince the start of the Covid-19
OL,17,Foutbreak.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
