OL,3,CUK net migration hits lowest level
OL,4,Csince 2012, excluding pandemic
OL,6,FThe figures released by the Office for
OL,7,FNational Statistics on Thursday also
OL,8,Fshowed a 48% drop in net migration
OL,9,Fcompared to the previous year.
OL,11,FIn the year to March 2021 net
OL,12,Fmigration stood at 132,000, at a time
OL,13,Fwhen travel restrictions were still in
OL,14,Fplace to contain the virus and the
OL,15,Fpost-Brexit immigration system had
OL,16,Fbeen introduced.
OL,18,FThe continued fall in net migration is
OL,19,Fbeing driven by fewer people from
OL,20,Foutside the EU arriving in the UK for
OL,21,Fwork, the ONS said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/4
