OL,3,CUK net migration hits lowest level
OL,4,Csince 2012, excluding pandemic
OL,6,FHome Office figures also released on
OL,7,FThursday showed a 12% drop in the
OL,8,Fnumber of people claiming asylum in
OL,9,Fthe UK.
OL,11,FIn the year from April 2025 to March
OL,12,F2026, the number of people claiming
OL,13,Fasylum was 93,525.
OL,15,FThere has also been a 35% drop in the
OL,16,Fnumber of asylum seekers in hotel
OL,17,Faccommodation, with a new low of
OL,18,F21,000 living in hotels in the year to
OL,19,FMarch 2026.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/4
